---
// About component for Elsan Transformers
---

<section id="about" class="py-10 bg-white overflow-hidden" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:about-section">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:39jdrn">
    <div class="max-w-4xl" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:39jdro">
      
      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="reveal-up" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:content">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:about-us-tag">
      <div class="w-8 h-[3px] bg-[#E85D1A]" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:line"></div>
      <span class="text-[15px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#E85D1A]" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:tag-text">About Us</span>
      </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-black mb-10 leading-[1.1] tracking-tighter text-slate-900" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:kdoahl">
          High Efficiency & <br/>
          <span class="text-slate-900" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:7m5i0x">High Performance —</span> <br/>
          Built Into Every <br/>
          Transformer
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-[15px]" data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:description-text">
          <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:p1">
            Elsan Transformer is a Turkish manufacturer of high-efficiency power and distribution transformers, bringing internationally certified engineering excellence to utilities, electrical distribution companies, industrial plants, and infrastructure developers across Nigeria and the wider West African region. Founded in 2018 and manufactured in Turkey to IEC 60076 and ISO 9001 standards, Elsan transformers are precision-engineered to perform reliably under tropical grid conditions — high ambient temperatures, humidity, voltage fluctuation, and the demanding load profiles common across West African power networks.
          </p>
          <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:p2">In a relatively short time, we have built a strong reputation for delivering high-quality, reliable, and efficient transformer solutions that meet the power needs of some of Nigeria's most demanding grid and industrial environments. Our manufacturing range covers distribution transformers from 25 kVA to 2,500 kVA and power transformers from 3.15 MVA to 50 MVA — one of the broadest product ranges available from a single manufacturer serving the West African market.</p>
          <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:p3">
            We understand the unique challenges of power infrastructure in Nigeria and across West Africa — from high ambient temperatures and harsh environmental conditions to the growing demand for reliable grid supply in both urban centres and rural communities. Every Elsan transformer is engineered specifically to perform reliably under these conditions, maximising energy efficiency, minimising losses, and delivering consistent output across varying load profiles.
          </p>
          <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:p4">
            At Elsan Transformer, quality is not an afterthought — it is built into every stage of our process, from design and material selection through to winding, assembly, and final testing. We adhere to IEC 60076 and ISO manufacturing standards to ensure that every transformer leaving our facility meets the requirements of Nigerian grid codes and international best practice.
          </p>
          <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:p5">
            We work closely with Electricity Distribution Companies (DISCOs), generation companies, industrial operators, and engineering contractors across Nigeria, Ghana, Cameroon, Benin Republic, Niger, and the broader West African region — providing tailored transformer solutions, expert technical support, and responsive after-sales service.
          </p>
          <p data-ps="src/components/home/About.astro:p6">
            Whether your project requires a standard distribution unit for a local feeder network or a fully custom-engineered power transformer for a major substation, our team is ready to help. Contact Elsan Transformer today and let us engineer the right solution for your power needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
